---
import H1 from '../components/ui/h1.astro';
import InfoLayout from '../layouts/InfoLayout.astro';
import ExternalLink from '../components/ui/external-link.astro';
---

<InfoLayout>
  <div
    class='p-4 sm:pt-8 sm:px-12 pb-20 min-h-dvh flex flex-col justify-between gap-32'
  >
    <section class='text-pretty text-zinc-300 space-y-4'>
      <H1 className='mb-4'> Hi, I'm April </H1>
      <article class='text-base space-y-2'>
        <p>
          I'm a <strong>full-stack developer</strong> specializing in Next.js and
          UI/UX. I work with Typescript, React, SQL, PHP, and various styling languages
          and libraries (Tailwind, SCSS, styled-components, MUI, shadcn).
        </p>
        <p>
          What began as a personal hobby quickly evolved into a full commitment
          to learning more about web technologies and design principles. I'm
          passionate about building thoughtful, user-friendly designs and
          functional web apps
        </p>
        <hr class='w-5 place-self-center text-zinc-600' />
        <p>
          Beyond programming, Iâ€™m into dance, linguistics, fashion, and classic
          role-playing games (cRPGs).
        </p>
        <p>
          Dance is my favourite movement-based activity, but I like yoga and calisthenics as well. My dream is to do a free handstand with ease and become good at tumbling.
        </p>
        <p>Also a big fan of cats and pigeons. I find them adorable.</p>
      </article>
      <figure>
        <img src='/me.webp' alt='April' class='w-full max-w-md rounded-lg' />
        <figcaption
          class='flex flex-row flex-wrap text-sm gap-1 text-zinc-500 my-1'
        >
          Photo taken by <ExternalLink
            className='text-sm'
            href='https://www.instagram.com/brightvibes.ca/'
            >Bright Vibes</ExternalLink
          >
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </section>
  </div>
</InfoLayout>
